'''Yamuna Pushkaram''' is a festival of [[Yamuna|River Yamuna]] normally occurs once in 12 years. This [[Pushkaram]] is observed for a period of 12 days from the time of entry of [[Jupiter]] into ''Karka'' rasi ([[Cancer (astrology)|Cancer]]).<ref>{{cite book |author=Roshen Dalal |title=Hinduism: An Alphabetical Guide |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=zrk0AwAAQBAJ&pg=PT921 |date=18 April 2014 |publisher=Penguin Books Limited |isbn=978-81-8475-277-9 |pages=921â}}</ref>
